
This is a template for creating a simple web application. 

It provides 

 * Easy starting up of the application
 * Hot-deployment from Eclipse: edit any Java file and Tomcat will reload 
   the app

== Prerequisites ==

export CATALINA_HOME=<wherever your Tomcat install is>
Or install apache-tomcat-6.0.32 side-by-side to this project

== How to run ==

Execute
  script/server.sh

then open browser at http://localhost:8080

